data.description: This 5-bedroom house has room for all your crew or room to grow!  The spacious and open living, dining, and kitchen areas are great for entertaining or family nights at home.  With its private, pool-sized yard, there is room for the kids and/or pets to roam, barbecues, or birthday parties.  With some recent interior and exterior paint, new backsplash, newer AC unit, and other updates, this home is ready for its new owners.  This home is located in a peaceful residential district just minutes from schools and shopping as well as easy access to bike trails.
